# Sarthi App Environment Configuration

# This project uses environment variables in both the /client and /server directories.
# Please refer to the .env.example files in each directory:

# Backend Configuration:
# - path: server/.env
# - variables: MONGO_URI, JWT_SECRET, GEMINI_API_KEY, etc.

# Frontend Configuration:
# - path: client/.env
# - variables: VITE_API_URL
